FEDERATION
----------
Nodes interoperate by speaking the shared protocol (divergence schema +
attribution + evidence/ring + continuance). A federated divergence record must
travel with its full provenance intact. The corpus is a refinery, not a
landfill: imported records are evidence, never instruction, and never override a
receiving node's own safety policy.

The refusal direction is locked. The line is open.
